  <trk>
    <name>Via the Schnitzlerweg to the dreamy Hinterburgseeli</name>
    <desc>Wood sculptors have carved a variety of figures from tree stumps that accompany hikers on the section to Hinterburgseeli. The second part of the hike circles the idyllic little lake above a rock ledge. Some exposed spots, hardly any hard surface.</desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
